1
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:14,259
So,

2
00:00:15,180 --> 00:00:17,219
it's not that I'll listen to you,

3
00:00:19,379 --> 00:00:21,419
but you have to listen to me.

4
00:00:31,179 --> 00:00:32,379
Be good.

5
00:01:04,779 --> 00:01:05,900
Why did you suddenly ask me out?

6
00:01:06,820 --> 00:01:07,659
Chengyan,

7
00:01:08,460 --> 00:01:10,380
you don't have to be so hostile to me.

8
00:01:11,219 --> 00:01:13,100
I haven't done anything wrong to you.

9
00:01:13,499 --> 00:01:14,419
If you have anything to say,

10
00:01:15,219 --> 00:01:16,219
just say it.

11
00:01:22,260 --> 00:01:24,180
I've always liked you.

12
00:01:25,180 --> 00:01:27,219
My feelings for you have never changed.

13
00:01:28,059 --> 00:01:29,579
But Ji Xiaoxue's appearance

14
00:01:30,340 --> 00:01:32,100
made me feel that we could never be together again.

15
00:01:34,579 --> 00:01:35,499
What about Chengjing?

16
00:01:36,620 --> 00:01:37,939
Did you abandon Chengjing?

17
00:01:38,820 --> 00:01:40,900
I never liked Gu Chengjing.

18
00:01:41,740 --> 00:01:43,219
If I don't marry you,

19
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:44,659
I won't choose him either.

20
00:01:44,779 --> 00:01:46,380
I just want to use the power of the Xia family

21
00:01:47,139 --> 00:01:47,939
to help you

22
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,299
solve the urgent problem of the Gu family.

23
00:01:55,540 --> 00:01:56,340
Is it because

24
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:59,939
you still can't let go of Ji Xiaoxue?

25
00:02:07,339 --> 00:02:08,899
Ji Xiaoxue is my sister now.

26
00:02:09,540 --> 00:02:11,260
I can't be with her anymore.

27
00:02:11,859 --> 00:02:13,299
I just want to help the Gu family

28
00:02:13,700 --> 00:02:14,579
get through this crisis.

29
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,579
I never thought

30
00:02:17,540 --> 00:02:19,100
we'd come full circle

31
00:02:19,459 --> 00:02:20,619
and end up back where we started.

32
00:02:24,579 --> 00:02:26,060
Isn't this a kind of fate?

33
00:02:32,060 --> 00:02:33,820
Xia Wanqing, what do you mean?

34
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:34,899
Auntie,

35
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:37,459
I voted for Gu Chengyan

36
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,380
for the long-term development of the Gu Group.

37
00:02:39,859 --> 00:02:40,820
I think it's fine.

38
00:02:41,459 --> 00:02:42,419
We had an agreement.

39
00:02:42,419 --> 00:02:44,220
No matter what agreement you had,

40
00:02:45,060 --> 00:02:47,380
I, as the chairman of the Gu Group,

41
00:02:47,780 --> 00:02:49,859
announce that I will hold a wedding

42
00:02:50,299 --> 00:02:51,299
with Ms. Xia Wanqing next week.

43
00:03:10,739 --> 00:03:12,220
I can't attend your wedding.

44
00:03:12,859 --> 00:03:14,859
I'm not planning to invite you anyway.

45
00:03:15,339 --> 00:03:17,299
Because I've discussed with the board

46
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:19,700
to kick you out of the Gu Group.

47
00:03:21,060 --> 00:03:22,060
On what grounds?

48
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:23,419
Don't forget,

49
00:03:23,739 --> 00:03:24,899
we still have

50
00:03:26,139 --> 00:03:27,100
shares in the company.

51
00:03:27,459 --> 00:03:29,100
Yeah, what gives you the right?

52
00:03:40,500 --> 00:03:42,940
For all the things you did to me before.

53
00:04:03,540 --> 00:04:04,579
Didn't you love me?

54
00:04:05,700 --> 00:04:07,019
Then why did you choose my brother?

55
00:04:07,619 --> 00:04:08,739
Why did you lie to me?

56
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:10,820
You said you loved me too,

57
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,139
but you're with Ji Xiaoxue.

58
00:04:20,060 --> 00:04:21,459
I don't love her at all.

59
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:23,500
I was just using her.

60
00:04:26,260 --> 00:04:27,019
Well,

61
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:28,899
I was using you too.

62
00:04:32,420 --> 00:04:33,139
So,

63
00:04:37,539 --> 00:04:39,019
you never loved me, right?

64
00:04:39,459 --> 00:04:40,700
If I loved you,

65
00:04:41,260 --> 00:04:43,380
I wouldn't have married your brother.

66
00:04:44,899 --> 00:04:45,940
I've always

67
00:04:46,500 --> 00:04:47,700
loved your brother.

68
00:04:54,940 --> 00:04:56,060
Don't be silly, brother.

69
00:05:11,139 --> 00:05:12,380
We put in so much effort,

70
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,579
yet we only get this little.

71
00:05:14,339 --> 00:05:15,139
Are you content with that?

72
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,500
It doesn't matter.

73
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:21,139
My father has always favored my brother.

74
00:05:21,979 --> 00:05:23,420
I could only follow behind them.

75
00:05:24,620 --> 00:05:26,139
I felt like nothing in the Gu family

76
00:05:26,139 --> 00:05:27,180
belonged to me.

77
00:05:28,339 --> 00:05:29,700
So I fought with all my might

78
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,099
to get what I wanted.

79
00:05:31,979 --> 00:05:32,740
But in the end,

80
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:35,860
what's not mine

81
00:05:37,019 --> 00:05:38,539
will never be mine.

82
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:00,740
Are you sure?

83
00:06:02,380 --> 00:06:03,180
I see.

84
00:06:11,380 --> 00:06:12,420
Can I come in?

85
00:06:14,740 --> 00:06:15,420
Of course.

86
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:21,579
Congratulations, Chairman Gu.

87
00:06:22,740 --> 00:06:23,779
Without your help,

88
00:06:24,099 --> 00:06:25,579
I'm not sure if I can be the chairman.

89
00:06:26,940 --> 00:06:27,740
No,

90
00:06:27,899 --> 00:06:29,219
thanks to Sister Wanqing.

91
00:06:29,620 --> 00:06:31,539
I knew she would support you.

92
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:33,620
From the first time I saw her,

93
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:35,060
I knew she liked you.

94
00:06:40,139 --> 00:06:41,060
I...

95
00:06:48,539 --> 00:06:49,539
I know she's a good girl.

96
00:06:50,579 --> 00:06:51,659
I won't let her down.

97
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,579
I also like her very much.

98
00:06:55,779 --> 00:06:56,500
By the way, brother,

99
00:06:56,620 --> 00:06:57,940
I'm going abroad soon.

100
00:06:59,620 --> 00:07:00,380
When?

101
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:01,979
In a couple of days.

102
00:07:02,459 --> 00:07:03,820
Will you attend

103
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:05,139
my wedding?

104
00:07:06,260 --> 00:07:07,500
Probably not.

105
00:07:07,820 --> 00:07:09,500
Mr. Gu has arranged a school for me,

106
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:10,620
so I can further my studies.

107
00:07:11,539 --> 00:07:13,339
I've never been abroad,

108
00:07:14,060 --> 00:07:15,060
and it's time for me to see the world.

109
00:07:16,339 --> 00:07:17,060
Fine.

110
00:07:18,139 --> 00:07:19,659
It doesn't matter whether I attend the wedding or not.

111
00:07:20,539 --> 00:07:21,740
I can still see you when I come back.

112
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:26,219
I'm here to wish you a happy marriage in advance.

113
00:07:27,019 --> 00:07:28,860
And to say goodbye to you.

114
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,620
I'll go first.

115
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,539
Okay.

116
00:08:43,780 --> 00:08:46,140
Do you take this man

117
00:08:46,339 --> 00:08:47,540
to be your lawful wedded husband,

118
00:08:48,259 --> 00:08:50,499
to have and to hold,

119
00:08:51,739 --> 00:08:53,379
for better or for worse,

120
00:08:54,259 --> 00:08:56,420
in sickness and in health,

121
00:08:57,379 --> 00:08:59,420
or for any other reason,

122
00:09:00,259 --> 00:09:02,820
to love, cherish,

123
00:09:03,099 --> 00:09:05,099
respect, and accept him,

124
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:08,219
and remain faithful to him

125
00:09:08,219 --> 00:09:10,219
until the end of your life?

126
00:09:10,379 --> 00:09:11,579
Do you take him?

127
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:20,780
I don't.
